        <title type="html">[ANNOUNCE] Apache NetBeans Has Graduated!</title>
        <author><name>Geertjan</name></author>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://blogs.apache.org/netbeans/entry/announce-apache-netbeans-has-graduated"/>
