        <category term="General" label="General" />
        <content type="html">The first of a series of informal virtual meetups took place today.

&lt;p&gt;The audio of the meeting is available here and takes about an hour:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tibK6A8CzYs&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tibK6A8CzYs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
